snippet.textDisplay: OCD is a debilitating psychological disorder. You have intrusive thoughts that you cannot control, and feel such a strong urge to do certain actions even though you really do not want to. Only then do you feel some temporary relief. OCD is NOT being someone who is very clean, neat and organized and ENJOYS being that way.

snippet.textDisplay: They're confusing OCD with perfectionism. Its possible to have both at the same time but they're not the same thing. I think Khloe is a classic perfectionist who exerts control at home to overcompensate for the  "messy" situations she's been in and "messy" relationships she's had that broke her down, so now she "cleans" everything. Note how Kris said her cleanings gotten worse recently...cough Tristan cough... One isn't worse than the other, my point is to not self diagnose or misdiagnose with unqualified family members and dodgy therapists on TV, and get the help that's really needed.
